Dia. 01 Big Damage
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is sente.
\par If White plays elsewhere (if doesn't defend) Black cuts at 1 and White's damage is big.
\par
\par Therefore White should defend at 1.
\par
\par Sente means that if the opponent doesn't answer he will end up in big damage.
\par
\par If it is so-
