Dia. 02 Gote Means?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Gote means that even if the opponent ignores your move, it doesn't matter.
\par
\par So if the damage is small he is going to play elsewhere.
\par
\par White's shape in the corner is a bit different this time.
\par Check White \'a1\'e2 carefully.
\par
\par }
