Dia. 03 Gote Endgame
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After Black 1 and 3, Black doesn't have any follow up.
\par
\par White doesn't have weak point, so White plays elsewhere and Black can't make any damage.
\par
\par Black 1 and 3 is called \cf1\b gote endgame\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
